<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q21_v6" title="Q21_v6" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceB</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float">
    <qti-default-value>
      <qti-value>0</qti-value>
    </qti-default-value>
  </qti-outcome-declaration>
  <qti-item-body>
    <p>En el diseño de un jardín, la longitud de un sendero se expresa como 
      <m:math>
        <m:mfrac>
          <m:msqrt><m:mn>72</m:mn></m:msqrt>
          <m:msqrt><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msqrt>
        </m:mfrac>
      </m:math>
      metros. Para facilitar los cálculos, se quiere escribir esa longitud como un número sin raíces. ¿Cuál de los siguientes números representa la misma longitud?
    </p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="false" max-choices="1">
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">
        <m:math>
          <m:mn>36</m:mn>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. La expresión dada no es <m:math><m:mn>36</m:mn></m:math>. Como <m:math><m:mn>72</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>36</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:math>, se tiene <m:math><m:msqrt><m:mn>72</m:mn></m:msqrt><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:msqrt><m:mn>36</m:mn></m:msqrt><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:msqrt><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msqrt><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>6</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:math>. Luego, al dividir <m:math><m:mn>6</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:math> por <m:math><m:msqrt><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:math>, el resultado es <m:math><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:math>, no <m:math><m:mn>36</m:mn></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">
        <m:math>
          <m:mn>6</m:mn>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! Como <m:math><m:mn>72</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>36</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:math>, entonces <m:math><m:msqrt><m:mn>72</m:mn></m:msqrt><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>6</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:math>. Al dividir <m:math><m:mn>6</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:math> por <m:math><m:msqrt><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:math>, queda <m:math><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:math>. Por eso la longitud equivale a <m:math><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:math> metros.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">
        <m:math>
          <m:msqrt><m:mn>36</m:mn></m:msqrt>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Esta opción todavía tiene una raíz y el enunciado pide escribir la longitud como un número sin raíces. Además, <m:math><m:msqrt><m:mn>36</m:mn></m:msqrt><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:math>, y la expresión original también vale <m:math><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:math>. Por lo tanto, esta alternativa no representa el resultado en la forma pedida.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">
        <m:math>
          <m:mn>12</m:mn>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. La expresión dada no vale <m:math><m:mn>12</m:mn></m:math>. Como <m:math><m:mn>72</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>36</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:math>, se obtiene <m:math><m:msqrt><m:mn>72</m:mn></m:msqrt><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>6</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:math>. Luego, <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mn>6</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow><m:msqrt><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:math>. Entonces <m:math><m:mn>12</m:mn></m:math> no representa la misma longitud.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Reescribir el número dentro de la raíz</strong></p>
            <p>Observamos que:</p>
            <m:math>
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mn>72</m:mn>
                <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                <m:mn>36</m:mn>
                <m:mo>×</m:mo>
                <m:mn>2</m:mn>
              </m:mrow>
            </m:math>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Simplificar la raíz del numerador</strong></p>
            <p>Usamos que:</p>
            <m:math>
              <m:mrow>
                <m:msqrt>
                  <m:mrow>
                    <m:mn>36</m:mn>
                    <m:mo>×</m:mo>
                    <m:mn>2</m:mn>
                  </m:mrow>
                </m:msqrt>
                <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                <m:msqrt><m:mn>36</m:mn></m:msqrt>
                <m:mo>×</m:mo>
                <m:msqrt><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msqrt>
              </m:mrow>
            </m:math>
            <p>Entonces:</p>
            <m:math>
              <m:mrow>
                <m:msqrt><m:mn>72</m:mn></m:msqrt>
                <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                <m:msqrt><m:mrow><m:mn>36</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msqrt>
                <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                <m:msqrt><m:mn>36</m:mn></m:msqrt>
                <m:mo>×</m:mo>
                <m:msqrt><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msqrt>
                <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                <m:mn>6</m:mn>
                <m:msqrt><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msqrt>
              </m:mrow>
            </m:math>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Reemplazar en la fracción original</strong></p>
            <m:math>
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mfrac>
                  <m:msqrt><m:mn>72</m:mn></m:msqrt>
                  <m:msqrt><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msqrt>
                </m:mfrac>
                <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                <m:mfrac>
                  <m:mrow>
                    <m:mn>6</m:mn>
                    <m:msqrt><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msqrt>
                  </m:mrow>
                  <m:msqrt><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msqrt>
                </m:mfrac>
              </m:mrow>
            </m:math>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 4: Simplificar el factor común</strong></p>
            <p>Como el numerador y el denominador tienen el factor <m:math><m:msqrt><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:math>, se cancela:</p>
            <m:math>
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mfrac>
                  <m:mrow>
                    <m:mn>6</m:mn>
                    <m:msqrt><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msqrt>
                  </m:mrow>
                  <m:msqrt><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msqrt>
                </m:mfrac>
                <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                <m:mn>6</m:mn>
              </m:mrow>
            </m:math>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>La longitud del sendero, escrita como un número sin raíces, es:</p>
            <m:math>
              <m:mn>6</m:mn>
            </m:math>
            <p>Por lo tanto, la alternativa correcta es <strong>B</strong>.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>